name: The Trial - Chapter One: Josephs Room
description:
Inspired by the first chapter of Franz Kafka's novel The Trial.

Explore the room of Joseph K. by diving into a creepy and ambiguous world, loaded with beautiful atmospheric music and voices.

Navigate through the scenes with left/right cursor keys, press numbers 1-8 to jump between scenes, scroll with your mouse wheel/trackbad or simply click once and let it all play for you.

Visuals by @yakudoo. Music, voices and sound effects by @1x1_NFT and @julesmaxmusic
